name: Nightmare realm...Another step. Acrylic painting.
description:
A4 acrylic painting. original M.A.D wew

will be framed and comes with 10 hand drawn stickers and art card with poem and painting description.

Another step another dimension, As the bunny travels and warps within in each realm he walks, the nightmare is the reality.

name: horror cliche 'Save Master'. Canvas and stickers
description:
Mixed media canvas 30x 40

plus 10 free assorted hand drawn stickers and artcard.

M.A.D wew birmingham street artist and sticker artist.
Protest bunny has been protesting and exploring.

This canvas is from the horror cliche protest collection. This one is the frankenstein 'Save Master' protestor bunny.
